summary: This is an email from an unspecified sender to the FBI New York field office, dated August 25, 2021, with attachments containing a conversation. The email includes a warning that the attached zip file cannot be opened on a phone due to security restrictions.

events.title: Email to FBI NY with Attachments
events.description: An email was sent to the FBI New York field office containing attachments described as a conversation. The email includes a security warning about the attached zip file.

keyFacts: An email was sent to the FBI New York field office on August 25, 2021.
The email contained attachments described as a conversation between unspecified individuals.
A security warning was included stating the attached zip file could not be opened on a phone due to restrictions.
The document is part of the Epstein case data set (Set 9) and is identified as EFTA00146956.
